<!DOCTYPE html><html><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><title>Equivalencia de Tasas</title><link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/styles.css"><link rel="icon" href="/img/Icon.ico"></head><body>@include('pages.partials.header')<main class="container"><h2 class="calc-title">Equivalencia de Tasas</h2><p class="calc-subtitle">Encuentra la tasa efectiva equivalente entre dos periodos distintos.</p><div class="formula">(1 + i₁)^m¹ = (1 + i₂)^m²</div><section class="panel-grid"><div class="card"><div class="field"><label>Tasa efectiva conocida</label><div class="input-wrap"><input id="i1" type="number"><span>%</span></div></div><div class="field mt"><label>Periodo de origen</label><select id="p1"><option>Mensual</option><option>Bimestral</option><option>Trimestral</option><option>Semestral</option><option>Anual</option></select></div><div class="field mt"><label>Periodo destino</label><select id="p2"><option>Trimestral</option><option>Mensual</option><option>Bimestral</option><option>Semestral</option><option>Anual</option></select></div><div class="mt"><button id="calc-equiv">Calcular equivalencia</button></div></div><div class="card result-card"><div><div>Ingresa los datos y presiona Calcular para ver el resultado.</div><div id="result" class="result-value"></div></div></div></section></main>@include('pages.partials.footer')<script src="/js/calculadora.js"></script></body></html>
